472
00:31:58,860 --> 00:32:01,820
Napanood ko si Choi noong Songkran,

473
00:32:01,860 --> 00:32:03,880
at parang gusto ko ring magsaya kahit papaano.

474
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:06,200
Kumusta ka, Phop?

475
00:32:06,980 --> 00:32:08,360
Ano ang dapat mong isuot para sa iyong pagbabalatkayo?

476
00:32:10,150 --> 00:32:12,500
Euang, mayroon ka bang mga kasuotan ng Farangi?

477
00:32:32,940 --> 00:32:34,760
Hindi mo kailangang magsuot ng ganyang kasuotan.

478
00:32:36,300 --> 00:32:37,390
May isa

479
