na para bang ibang tao ka na.

659
00:44:41,230 --> 00:44:42,360
Kung gayon bakit...

660
00:44:42,660 --> 00:44:44,480
Ayaw mo bang tumigil sa paghabol sa akin?!

661
00:44:47,120 --> 00:44:49,920
Ano ba ang naaalala mo, Klao?

662
00:44:51,030 --> 00:44:52,240
Isa na namang away, 'di ba?!

663
00:44:52,810 --> 00:44:54,360
Cherd! Klao! Tumayo ka!

664
00:44:59,320 --> 00:45:00,040
Cherd!

665
00:45:01,980 --> 00:45:02,560
Cherd!!

666
00:45:02,910 --> 00:45:03,480
Oo.

667
00:45:04,190 --> 00:45:06,360
Walang araw na lumilipas nang hindi ka nag-aaway.

668
00:45:06,760 --> 00:45:08,880
Huwag mo akong piliting pagbawalan ka
sa lugar na ito magpakailanman.

669
00:45:11,520 --> 00:45:12,360
Mahal na Klao.

670
00:45:12,620 --> 00:45:13,720
Bumalik ka agad sa iyong mansyon,

671
00:45:14,060 --> 00:45:15,120
